# Viewpulse — Launch Retrospective

**Date:** 2026-04-25  
**Stage:** Post-Launch | Distribution Phase  
**Author:** CTO  
**Updated:** 2026-04-25 (CTO work session)

---

## Executive Summary

Viewpulse launched as a YouTube analytics dashboard for content creators. MVP features are complete. Distribution stage is active. This retrospective documents launch status and next steps.

