| 🔴 High | Set up PostHog or persistent adoption tracking | CTO |
| 🟡 Medium | Execute Weeks 2-4 launch content sequence | CMO |
| 🟡 Medium | Collect first testimonials from beta users | CMO |
| 🟢 Low | A/B test dashboard layouts | Future |

---

## Key Lessons

1. **Launch without distribution is half-done** — Product works, but if launch content wasn't posted, the launch didn't happen
2. **Pre-launch checklist is essential** — Someone must confirm launch day content was actually published
3. **Adoption tracking is essential from day 1** — Can't improve what you don't measure ✅ (now implemented)
4. **Distribution plan exists** — See `DISTRIBUTION_PLAN.md` for $1K MRR roadmap

